Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_cppr_s...matched_clocks(25.10)    timing_cppr_s...matched_clocks(25.10)

Name
       timing_cppr_skip_clock_reconvergence_for_unmatched_clocks

Syntax
       timing_cppr_skip_clock_reconvergence_for_unmatched_clocks    {true    |
       false}

       Default: false

       Allows the software to skip re-convergence of unmatched clocks.

       When set to true, the software uses the farthest branch point from  the
       register clock pins when the launching and capturing clocks are differ-
       ent - the re-converge points are ignored and not searched.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

